dc_description_s: This polygon shapefile represents National Parks, National Forests, State and local parks and forests within the United States at 1:100,000 scale. This layer is part of the 2014 ESRI Data and Maps collection for ArcGIS 10.2.U.S. Major Parks provides thousands of named parks and forests at National, State, and local levels.
